    <title>服务器连接与管理指南</title>
    <link href="/ruiBlog/2025/04/01/npusetting/"/>
    <url>/ruiBlog/2025/04/01/npusetting/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="服务器连接与管理指南"><a href="#服务器连接与管理指南" class="headerlink" title="服务器连接与管理指南"></a>服务器连接与管理指南</h1><h3 id="登录服务器"><a href="#登录服务器" class="headerlink" title="登录服务器"></a><strong>登录服务器</strong></h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ssh root@172.20.18.7<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Docker-相关"><a href="#Docker-相关" class="headerlink" title="Docker 相关"></a><strong>Docker 相关</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>进入容器</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker <span class="hljs-built_in">exec</span> -it 910B /bin<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>模型路径</strong><ul><li><code>910B_MindIE</code> → <code>qwen2.0</code></li><li><code>910B</code> → <code>deepseek_distill_qwen</code></li></ul></li><li><strong>MindIE 配置文件路径</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">/Ascend/mindie/latest/mindie-service/conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="后台运行-Python-脚本"><a href="#后台运行-Python-脚本" class="headerlink" title="后台运行 Python 脚本"></a><strong>后台运行 Python 脚本</strong></h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">nohup</span> python extract.llm_api_mobidfy_prompt_final_Marital_history.py &gt; output.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">nohup</span> python extract.llm_api_mobidfy_prompt_final_Specialist_examination.py &gt; output.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">nohup</span> python extract.llm_api_mobidfy_prompt_final_family_history.py &amp;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="进程管理"><a href="#进程管理" class="headerlink" title="进程管理"></a><strong>进程管理</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>查看进程</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ps aux | grep extract.llm_api_mobidfy_prompt_final_Marital_history.py<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>查找进程</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pgrep -fl extract.llm_api_mobidfy_prompt_final_Marital_history.py<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>终止进程</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">kill</span> 68201<br><span class="hljs-built_in">kill</span> -9 68201  <span class="hljs-comment"># 强制终止</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="SSH-公私钥配置"><a href="#SSH-公私钥配置" class="headerlink" title="SSH 公私钥配置"></a><strong>SSH 公私钥配置</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>生成 SSH 密钥</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ssh-keygen -t ed25519<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>追加公钥</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> id_ed25519.pub &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/authorized_keys<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>本地主机私钥路径</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plaintext">C:\Users\25020\.ssh\id_ed25519<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="服务器管理"><a href="#服务器管理" class="headerlink" title="服务器管理"></a><strong>服务器管理</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>重启服务器</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">reboot<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="MindIE-服务"><a href="#MindIE-服务" class="headerlink" title="MindIE 服务"></a><strong>MindIE 服务</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>启动 MindIE</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./mindiedemo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>查看端口监听</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">netstat -tulnp | grep 1025<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">tcp</span>        <span class="hljs-number">0</span>      <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1:1025</span>          <span class="hljs-number">0.0.0.0</span>:*               LISTEN      <span class="hljs-number">1848</span>/./bin/mindiese<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
