    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Cancer-Risk-Assessment-Tools"><a href="#Cancer-Risk-Assessment-Tools" class="headerlink" title="Cancer Risk Assessment Tools"></a>Cancer Risk Assessment Tools</h1><p>Here are some useful cancer risk assessment tools from various institutions:</p><h2 id="🏥-Beijing-Cancer-Hospital-Genetic-Research-Lab"><a href="#🏥-Beijing-Cancer-Hospital-Genetic-Research-Lab" class="headerlink" title="🏥 Beijing Cancer Hospital - Genetic Research Lab"></a>🏥 Beijing Cancer Hospital - Genetic Research Lab</h2><ul><li><strong>Esophageal Cancer Prediction Tool</strong><ul><li><a href="https://fxpg.bjcancer.org/ecms/ptools/ec.html">Visit the tool</a></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="🇭🇰-Hong-Kong-Cancer-Fund"><a href="#🇭🇰-Hong-Kong-Cancer-Fund" class="headerlink" title="🇭🇰 Hong Kong Cancer Fund"></a>🇭🇰 Hong Kong Cancer Fund</h2><ul><li><strong>Breast Cancer Risk Assessment Tool</strong><ul><li><a href="https://www.cancer.gov.hk/sc/bctool/index.html">Visit the tool</a></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="🏥-Nanjing-Medical-University"><a href="#🏥-Nanjing-Medical-University" class="headerlink" title="🏥 Nanjing Medical University"></a>🏥 Nanjing Medical University</h2><ul><li><strong>Lung Cancer Risk Assessment Tool</strong><ul><li><a href="http://ccra.njmu.edu.cn/lckey/web">Visit the tool</a></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="🌍-Other-Risk-Calculation-Tools"><a href="#🌍-Other-Risk-Calculation-Tools" class="headerlink" title="🌍 Other Risk Calculation Tools"></a>🌍 Other Risk Calculation Tools</h2><ul><li><strong>General Risk Calculation Platform</strong>: <a href="https://riskcalc.org/">RiskCalc</a></li><li><strong>U.S. Breast Cancer Risk Assessment Tool</strong>: <a href="https://bcrisktool.cancer.gov/calculator.html">BCRiskTool</a></li></ul><p>These tools can help estimate cancer risks based on different factors, supporting early detection and prevention strategies.  </p>]]></content>
    
    
    
